Package bio.singa.core.utility

Interface Bounded<BoundType extends java.lang.Comparable<BoundType>>

  • Type Parameters:
    BoundType - The Type of the bound. Has to be Comparable.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleInterval, IntegerInterval, Range
    public interface Bounded<BoundType extends java.lang.Comparable<BoundType>>
    Defines a Object to be bounded by a lower and upper bound. The upper and the lower bound should be specified upon Object creation. Afterwards it is possible to check whether an Object of the given Type is in between both bounds.
